{"id":"47eb91ee6593d6eb1c3d01a029e5b5a8af7f367a87c50ae67bf358f5d6403886","item_id":"26e081190c:0","text":"带有金属闪片和涂层的车漆。"}
{"id":"94b344e3a85b8b4252bc22d8176ed0f56ded00ec42a23edfc2396740f988f86c","item_id":"26e081190c:1","text":"生成一个凹凸法线，用于在高光或反射材质效果中模拟类似闪片的结果。将它连接到 PxrSurface 的 Bump Normal 参数，可以创建金属闪片车漆。"}
{"id":"5623398d54781bd64929648b12ce690f0a248c8cba6dcd57b88c37559630b38f","item_id":"26e081190c:3","text":"Input Normal"}
{"id":"719aff542f7d4b6dd4d489ac8b0a27f584eb78d2dddc02c4ad1b68e7dfce48cf","item_id":"26e081190c:4","text":"如果希望在已有 bump pattern 之上叠加闪片，请在此连接。未连接时会忽略。"}
{"id":"dc7141c66b2d140813ed7fec612546090ac8d40941cdc71ed79faddbee6302dd","item_id":"26e081190c:5","text":"Flake Randomness"}
{"id":"9a3542b72ddd50840764af88525bda421c79732155518da071a4a96fb5be4185","item_id":"26e081190c:6","text":"增加闪片法线的分布范围，或者说增加它们相对于基础法线的偏离程度。"}
{"id":"a73434803d67a5180cc56b5d0fff313e09e454a5804167fb526b399372401a97","item_id":"26e081190c:7","text":"Flake Frequency"}
{"id":"9bfc8705077721254940cfa1c711c1ca73eab922fd54679a2f257b2eb3d200fa","item_id":"26e081190c:8","text":"改变金属闪片特征的 global（全局）尺寸。"}
{"id":"896fd1bab29b6ab7ba0f7851c547f6b9af30a5b2a5f26684e4e36fec0c8ecbd7","item_id":"26e081190c:9","text":"Flake Density"}
{"id":"d9592d3174a42ab96602cf5398db3ae5815920ba07415379521c1b649cb4c1d9","item_id":"26e081190c:10","text":"改变给定面积内金属闪片的数量。有效范围为 0（无闪片）到 1（全部为闪片）。"}
{"id":"8d9e3f0d3a05547b0651acf3374a73113b88160d53bbcfe54eb7e4ec7fe1d923","item_id":"26e081190c:11","text":"Flake Size"}
{"id":"d1cb353496777615dd7f21131596907622a72a7923a58df26b9915ae176c1f47","item_id":"26e081190c:12","text":"改变金属闪片的尺寸。将数值推到 1 以上会产生类似镀锌金属的效果。"}
{"id":"2a4d057d4ae16c9e95f2f7234757b39dfaa85eb166decda58880b1b69d809511","item_id":"26e081190c:13","text":"Octaves"}
{"id":"1b230e8e449929ca3dac910dd92bc8d878cf5a043e33a0250fbc9b0bd571c2d2","item_id":"26e081190c:14","text":"用于计算闪片的噪声 octave 数。大多数情况下，1 就足够。"}
{"id":"91fbe4c855fbe0759f01c98185f0e5b1317146f3371bb32e0470f226ac26f42b","item_id":"26e081190c:15","text":"Jitter"}
{"id":"f74e6ef97d3f61794c669b1886b8a34793d8f659a220254579a4f3fe0f2765db","item_id":"26e081190c:16","text":"抖动闪片的位置。0.0 会产生网格状排列，1.0 看起来非常随机。"}
{"id":"90af7edbab0be080d4d87a04f25de30740310b22f04511eab67c8995e083c203","item_id":"26e081190c:17","text":"Validate Normals"}
{"id":"c167eb7de62ce885645371e8f3717f61ff90a5a45626dc919573f60597e3580b","item_id":"26e081190c:18","text":"确保闪片法线始终与原始法线位于同一半球。"}
{"id":"86c48a7a8d8bfe6f03ae35f27ab7a28d529bbfc956aab18678fc4690f7941427","item_id":"26e081190c:19","text":"Match C++ patterns"}
{"id":"44a45059c8a98accfc5bbb1ca6f7a8e60ec0cb62ee8bf8b2b32c427f6328fd05","item_id":"26e081190c:20","text":"匹配 RenderMan 23 C++ 场景，但可能会拖慢渲染。仅在必要时使用。"}
{"id":"9fc06bb5e3abd082bac66b70d918ccdbae514011649060082138bd6debd3dbde","item_id":"26e081190c:22","text":"应用闪片所使用的 manifold。"}
{"id":"eb2e96f887d34d1e8a31d4000cf5f02c65570626319e4a582d04dc119742c403","item_id":"26e081190c:23","text":"默认情况下（没有连接 manifold 时）为"}
{"id":"582967534d0f909d196b97f9e6921342777aea87b46fa52df165389db1fb8ccf","item_id":"26e081190c:24","text":"在"}
{"id":"2958d416d08aa5a472d7b509036cb7eafd542add84527e66a145ea64cb4cdc75","item_id":"26e081190c:25","text":"object"}
{"id":"e28b267c0c5db8e7457519e0f475886fbbf6bff796051e56dc5990dfd7c55224","item_id":"26e081190c:26","text":"空间中。如果对象没有变形，这样就可以正常工作。"}
{"id":"e1ff5e4e65b1e253c3dbfbd6fa1edbdda59b8af9b6fb8acdc03615fee7e30e37","item_id":"26e081190c:27","text":"如果对象会变形："}
{"id":"394ad457e01d9636e3fbc61306dc68b117fa18d3bf7d8dea99dd136cd04b6466","item_id":"26e081190c:28","text":"Add（添加）一个"}
{"id":"2c5cacbb0fdf112ad145babc013073931678c2f4a88c34e6de03afd61b3935a9","item_id":"26e081190c:29","text":"primvar 到几何体的未变形状态。"}
{"id":"a2a769e959cfd33c6744a4099fd4d901e8e2814f5dce4ca3f330aece5991d1ef","item_id":"26e081190c:30","text":"创建一个"}
{"id":"0d6a89778d4ff54d52144613b2c76eb53b520f287aebac0b8b279a36f9c3701c","item_id":"26e081190c:31","text":"PxrManifold3D"}
{"id":"8d197eda8a12b0e54abb40a06d9a12c9ec3b36dd29fbc153708e6e4d080a7547","item_id":"26e081190c:32","text":"节点，并将其连接到"}
{"id":"bbed8964e7b9380defeb4e0fa4b8460df310304035c8c0570d1091620932a6a4","item_id":"26e081190c:33","text":"PxrFlakes"}
{"id":"bb853680249ae0d0b2608016760e0147668a6db1229576b8b27fa4d5142d609f","item_id":"26e081190c:34","text":"节点。"}
{"id":"7235be45c6659300498dccd46ee4a3370aa5a02f2e8e8a7f67526d259799b4a2","item_id":"26e081190c:38","text":"在 manifold 的"}
{"id":"7235be45c6659300498dccd46ee4a3370aa5a02f2e8e8a7f67526d259799b4a2","text":"在 manifold 的"}
{"id":"6da94174e57953caefa056edbe4464a689cba8828d28db8677be5eeb0fe0fc0e","item_id":"26e081190c:36","text":"Pref"}
{"id":"f7ee3091b1a1a1493c7002c1339eafa70abc670da047c8ce2c3343dd76497bfa","item_id":"26e081190c:40","text":"字段中输入："}
{"id":"f7ee3091b1a1a1493c7002c1339eafa70abc670da047c8ce2c3343dd76497bfa","text":"字段中输入："}
{"id":"b514ebf73921fea11670ca9640e96c27bc4e980867839d368eca5bd872bd174f","item_id":"26e081190c:39","text":"Coordinate System"}
{"id":"7f69e5947418b1555a1d48ccadf50f5f065a7b50d03def2e60f0470abde48413","item_id":"26e081190c:42","text":"resultN"}
{"id":"a0cff1de29adcb01a849ee0489d4d936508f384a733425f52237b4f28e65fdcb","item_id":"26e081190c:43","text":"凹凸法线。"}
{"id":"890f7aa1b6882bd3a2548401dd7ae638108b8010a3cbcc25974c005ba36f3048","item_id":"26e081190c:44","text":"resultA"}
{"id":"205914c0606e3ef8048d6d73e9ba9fed692ad4f5a254b43aa72fd4560671b026","item_id":"26e081190c:45","text":"闪片的 mask。这是一个黑白 mask，例如可用于给闪片着色或改变其 roughness。"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "26e081190c:2", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "e29793dea8429f58cc913ce697117a3614eaa231b5a3942af954b66c44d43850", "item_id": "26e081190c:21", "text": "Manifold"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "26e081190c:41", "text": "Output Parameters（输出参数）"}
